          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Does dropshipping actually work in Lebanon?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">When lots of people on the internet were saying that "Dropshipping is dead" or "doesn't work in any arab country", they meant the old dropshipping model where you have to gamble with your money on products hoping they might sell while paying huge fees. With Droparabia however, the game has changed. Now all you need is a small budget to run your ads campaign and Droparabia will take care of sourcing hundreds of different products for you and handle order fulfillment while you focus on scaling your business.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Dropshipping can be competitive, how do I succeed?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
